title: PRIYANKA CHOPRA JONAS
description: Actress, writer and humanitarian Priyanka Chopra Jonas is one of the most recognizable faces in the world. She discusses her journey of self-discovery, her marriage to Nick Jonas and her New York Times bestselling memoir, Unfinished.
author: podcasts@own.oprah.com (Oprah)
